trans-unit.source: Represents the smart label properties of an annotation to store.
trans-unit.target: Representerer smart etiketten egenskaper for en merknad til å lagre.

trans-unit.source: This class is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle> class used for <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> objects.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen hentes fra det <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle>klassen som brukes <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle"></xref> class with the specified chart element.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle"> </xref> klassen med det angitte diagramelementet.

trans-unit.source: The chart element that this style belongs to.
trans-unit.target: Diagramelementet denne stilen tilhører.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the back color of the label callout.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bakgrunnsfarge for bildeforklaring for etiketten.

trans-unit.source: This property is only applicable when the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle*> property is set to a value of <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelCalloutStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen gjelder bare når den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle*>egenskapen settes til en verdi av <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelCalloutStyle"> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle*>

trans-unit.source: This property is for internal use and is hidden at design time and run time.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er gjelder internt hos skjult på utformingstidspunktet og kjøretid.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> object that represents the back color of the label callout.
